sentences: Rod Carrillo and Ronnie Sumrall are a British-American house music duo.
They have been producing and writing music together since 2007, after they met in Los Angeles.
They released a full-length album in 2010 entitled Rhythm, after the success of their previous singles.
They are perhaps best known for their songs: "Moonshine Rising", "Long Time" and "Breakin' Out",
